OL,5, A designer who said he was "made a     
OL,6, scapegoat" after Martin Bashir asked   
OL,7, him to forge documents in order to     
OL,8, secure an interview with Princess Diana
OL,9, has reached a settlement with the BBC. 
OL,11,FMatt Wiessler did not know how Mr      
OL,12,FBashir, then a Panorama reporter,      
OL,13,Fintended to use the faked statements.  
OL,15,FBut he later discovered executives had 
OL,16,Fdecided he would not work for the BBC  
OL,17,Fagain, effectively ending his career.  
OL,19,FThe BBC has apologised and said he     
OL,20,F"acted with complete integrity".       
